One can look at the situation like a glass half empty or a glass half full.Later, at around timestamp 30:00, he gave a little more information about what was causing their concern about the New World Order, which hopefully is not the jungle growing back.', "The New World Order Is Here, And America Isn't Part Of It #PayAttentionThe New World Order Is Here, A..."]

The founder of SpaceX, Tesla, Neuralink and other ambitious projects has become a symbol of the technological revolution. His ideas on creating a sustainable future for humanity, space exploration and the development of artificial intelligence have received worldwide recognition. However, like any major figure, Musk has become the subject of various conspiracy theories that span his personal life, business projects and influence on world of the most popular theories is that Musk is hiding the true goals of his projects, especially in the field of space. It is said that SpaceX is not just developing rocket technology for commercial launches, but is also working on creating technologies for the colonization of Mars to prepare humanity for a possible apocalypse on Earth. Many proponents of this theory suggest that Musk has access to secret information that confirms the inevitability of a global catastrophe, and that his mission is to create a Plan B for human the question of how much Musk really hides his real motives remains open. He himself claims that his ambitions are related to the desire to help humanity, and not to the creation of some kind of global conspiracy. But despite these statements, his actions sometimes arouse suspicion among the of the factors fueling conspiracy theories is also his relationship with government agencies. Musk actively cooperates with NASA, the US government, and also negotiates with other world powers on space research issues. Some critics believe that Musk actually works for the government, and his projects serve not only commercial purposes, but also the strategic interests of states, which adds even more secrecy to his addition, one cannot fail to mention his ideas in the field of artificial intelligence and neurotechnology, which cause no less controversy. In particular, the Neuralink project, which aims to connect the human brain with a computer, excites the imagination of many. Some believe that Musk is seeking to create technology that will allow him to control human consciousness, which means he has hidden plans to manipulate equally important element of the conspiracy theory is Musks personal life. Some argue that his marriages, divorces and relationships with high-profile figures are part of an elaborate strategy to create an image of an "inspiring genius" to divert attention from his real any case, no matter how plausible these theories are, Musk continues to be a controversial figure. For some, he is a brilliant innovator and a hero who can change the world.
